\id ECC
\h Ambarreḥ
\toc1 Ambarreḥ
\toc2 Ambarreḥ
\toc3 Amb.
\mt1 Ambarreḥ
\c 1
\s1 Aqa kuřci di řbaṭeř
\m 
\v 1 Awařen n Umbarreḥ, mmis n Dawud, ajeǧid di Urcalim.
\b
\m 
\v 2 D ibeṭṭařen qaɛ, iqqar Umbarreḥ, d ibeṭṭařen qaɛ, aqa kuřci di řbaṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Izhd. 62:10; 144:4\x*
\v 3 Man řefḍeř i iǧan ɣar bnadem di marra arber i zi ittmarret sadu tfuct? \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Amb. 2:22; 3:9\x*
\v 4 Jjiř iggur, ijj n jjiř \add nneɣni\add* ittas-dd, \add maca\add* tammurt ad teqqim tbedd i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Izhd. 104:5\x*
\v 5 Tneqqar-dd tfuct u tɣeǧi tfuct \add ɛawed\add*, \add xenni\add* ad dd-tedweř deɣya ɣar manis i dd-tneqqar.
\v 6 Iggur \add usemmiḍ\add* ɣar ljanub u ittenneḍ \add ɛawed\add* ɣar ccamal. Am iggur ittenneḍ, ittenneḍ usemmiḍ, uca ittɣima usemmiḍ iddakkwař-dd ɣar uduwwar nnes.
\v 7 Marra iɣezran ttkebban di řebḥar, \add maca\add* war ittccuri řebḥar. Ɣar manis dd-ttazzřen iɣezran, dinni ttɣimen ttazzřen \add ɛawed\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Ayub 38:8, 9, 10; Izhd. 104:9, 10\x*
\v 8 Marra timesřayin ssaḥařent \add břa qeṭṭu\add*, uřa d ijjen war izemmar ad xas yini ca. Ɛemmarṣ tiṭṭ ad tejjawen zeg weẓri uca amezzuɣ ɛemmarṣ ad ijjawen zeg utesři.
\v 9 Min tuɣa iǧan ad yiři, min ittwaggen ad ittwagg \add ɛawed\add*. War \add din\add* iǧi jdid sadu tfuct. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Amb. 3:15\x*
\v 10 Ma aqa din ca n řḥajjet qqaren xas: “Xzar, man aya d jdid!”?, aqa-tt din di zzmanat nni tuɣa iǧan qbeř i neccin.
\v 11 War din ǧin d ixarriṣen x yinni tuɣa d imezwura, uca uřa x yinni i ɣa yiřin d ineggura, war xasen ttiřin ixarriṣen ɣar yinni dd ɣa yasen awarni asen \add ɛad\add*.
\b
\s1 Tarezzut n Umbarreḥ
\m 
\v 12 Necc, Ambarreḥ, tuɣa ayi d ajeǧid x Israil, di Urcalim.
\v 13 Necc tuɣa kkseɣ deg wuř inu ad arzuɣ u ad beqqceɣ s tiɣit di marra min imsaren sadu ujenna. Man aya d ijj n ccɣeř iwɛar, iwca i-t AREBBI i tarwa n bnadem ḥima ad dayes řhan.
\v 14 Necc ẓriɣ marra timegga i ittwaggen sadu tfuct, u xzar, marra aya tuɣa-t di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\v 15 Min ifarɣen war izemmar ad ittwaseggem, u min ittxeṣṣan war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb.
\v 16 Necc nniɣ deg wuř inu: “Xzar, necc ssemɣareɣ tiɣit inu uca arniɣ dayes, mahu marra inni tuɣa izeddɣen di Urcalim qbeř inu. Uř inu iẓra aṭṭas n tiɣit d tussna.
\v 17 Necc ggiɣ uř inu, maḥend ad dd-awyeɣ tiɣit, \add maḥend\add* ad ssneɣ tubbuheřya d jjheř. Necc ufiɣ uřa d man aya aqa d aḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\v 18 Maɣar deg waṭṭas n tiɣit, dayes aṭṭas n řhemm, u wenni yarennin di tussna, yarenni deg wemnus.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Abarreɛ n tmesřayin n tudart
\m 
\v 1 Necc nniɣ deg wuř inu: “As-dd, ad cek qeǧbeɣ s řefraḥet. Xzar ɣar min icnan!” Ufiɣ uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Lk. 12:19\x*
\v 2 I tadeḥḥact nniɣ necc: “D tabuhařit \add cem\add*!”, u i řefraḥet: “Min dd ɣa tawi amenni?”
\v 3 Necc arzuɣ deg wuř inu umi ssareccaqeɣ arrimet inu s binu - di řweqt mani uř inu iqqim ittᵉṭṭef \add sřayem n tudart inu\add* s tiɣit - u umi qqimeɣ řessqeɣ di tubbuheřya\add -ya\add*, ařami ad ẓareɣ min iǧan ḥsen qaɛ i tarwa n bnadem, maḥend ad t ggen sadu ujenna am ḥessben s řmeqřub řqedd n wussan n tudart nsen.
\m 
\v 4 Necc arniɣ di řemɣaret n min ggiɣ. Necc ssbeddeɣ i yixef inu tudrin, ẓẓuɣ tizayarin deg imarjaɛen i yixef inu.
\v 5 Necc ggiɣ iḥwicen d iftisen am yinni n jjennet uca ẓẓuɣ daysen ɛřam kuř ticejjura n fruta.
\v 6 Necc ggiɣ iyeřmamen ccuren s waman ḥima ad zzaysen ssesweɣ azɣar, maḥend ad ssuffyent tcejjura. \f ◼ \fr 2:6 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 7 Necc sɣiɣ isemɣan d tiyya, uca dewřen ɣari imsexxaren ittwarwen di taddart \add inu\add*. Tuɣa ɣari uřa d ict n tḥimart d tameqqrant n ifunasen d wuǧi, aṭṭas x marra inni tuɣa iǧan di Urcalim qbeř xafi. \f ◼ \fr 2:7 \fk imsexxaren ittwarwen di taddart inu\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ayt n taddart’, ixs ad yini ‘isemɣan niɣ imsexxaren nni ittwarwen di taddart n bab nsen, war dd-ttwasɣen zi barra’. Ijj n umsexxar am wanita ittwaḥseb d amezwaru n marra isemɣan di taddart n sides.\f*
\v 8 Necc ssmuneɣ i yixef inu uřa d nnuqart d wureɣ d řeknuz n ijeǧiden u zi lɛamalat. Necc ḍebbareɣ-dd i yixef inu imeɣnujen d tmeɣnujin uřa d min di meẓren tarwa n bnadem: tamɣart d temɣarin.
\v 9 Necc arniɣ di řemɣaret inu uca arniɣ-dd aṭṭas, mahu marra inni iǧan qbeř i necc di Urcalim, \add maca\add* tiɣit teqqim tbedd akidi.
\v 10 Marra min iǧan d meẓri di tiṭṭawin inu, war d asent qḍiɛeɣ. War menɛeɣ i wuř inu uřa d ict n řḥajjet, maɣar uř inu ifarḥ zi ssibbet n marra tamara inu: ta d tasɣart n marra amarret inu.
\v 11 \add Xas uca\add* ggiɣ udem inu ɣar marra timegga inu, min ggin ifassen inu, u ɣar umarret nni ggiɣ am d ayi tuɣa ttmarrateɣ maḥend ad ggeɣ \add marra aya\add*. Xzar, \add ufiɣ\add* man aya marra aqa-t di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ uca war \add dayes\add* iǧi bu řefḍeř sadu tafuct.
\b
\s1 Tiɣit d tubbuheřya
\m 
\v 12 Necc ggiɣ udem inu maḥend ad ẓareɣ tiɣit, uřa d tubbuheřya d taɣyuři, maɣar min iɛna bnadem nni dd ɣa iḍfaren ajeǧid nni yareccḥen aṭṭas zeg wami? \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Amb. 1:17; 7:23\x*
\v 13 Necc ẓriɣ aqa tiɣit teɛdu x tubbuheřya, am teɛdu tfawt x taǧest.
\v 14 Amiɣis ɣares tiṭṭawin deg uzeǧif nnes, \add maca\add* abuhaři iggur di taǧest. \add Xenni\add* ufiɣ aqa třeqqef i-ten marra tira d ict.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ deg wuř inu: “Mařa teřqef abuhaři, ad teřqef uřa d necc. Mayemmi ɣa meyyzeɣ s tiɣit?” \add Uca\add* nniɣ deg wuř inu: “Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř.”
\v 16 Maɣar i řebda war ittiři řɛeqřan x umiɣis uřa x ubuhaři. Deg wussan i dd ɣa yasen ad ittwattu marra. Ma war immut umiɣis am ubuhaři?
\m 
\v 17 Uca bdiɣ ad carheɣ tudart, maɣar min ittwaggen sadu tafuct, tewḍa-dd xafi \add mɣir\add* d tamara, maɣar man aya marra aqa-t di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\v 18 Bdiɣ ɛawed ad carheɣ amarret inu i zi marrteɣ sadu tafuct, maḥend ad t jjeɣ i yijj n bnadem nni i ɣa yiřin awarni ayi.
\v 19 Wi issnen ma netta ad yiři d amiɣis niɣ d abuhaři? Aqa ggur ad iṣelleṭ x marra amarret inu i zi marrteɣ u i zi tuɣa ǧiɣ d amiɣis sadu tfuct. Aqa uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř.
\m 
\v 20 \add Řexdenni\add* nnqeřbeɣ ḥima ad ggeɣ uř inu ad iqneḍ x marra amarret inu i zi tuɣa marrteɣ sadu tfuct.
\v 21 Maɣar \add waxxa\add* aqa din ijj n bnadem i umi dd-yusa amarret nnes ak-d tiɣit d tussna d tzemmar, \add ɛad\add* ittxeṣṣa ac ad t iwc i yijj n bnadem i war imarrten i man aya. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř d ict n tuɛeffna d tameqqrant.
\v 22 Maɣar man řefḍeř ɣar bnadem zi marra amarret nnes u zi tarezzut n wuř nnes i zi ittmarrat sadu tfuct? \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Amb. 1:3; 3:9\x*
\v 23 Maɣar marra ussan nnes mɣir d amnus u ccɣeř nnes \add yiwiḍ\add* řhemm. Ɛad di ǧiřet war yareyyeḥ wuř nnes. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř.
\m 
\v 24 War din iǧi d lemliḥ i bnadem x macca d tseswit uřa x umi iɣebba řeɛmar nnes ɣar \add marra\add* amarret nnes. Necc ẓriɣ aqa uřa d man aya \add yusa-dd\add* zeg ufus n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Amb. 3:12, 22; 5:18; 8:15\x*
\v 25 Maɣar man wen izemmaren ad yecc niɣ man wen izemmaren ad yawi ařiqqi barra i Necc?
\v 26 Maɣar Netta ittic tiɣit d tussna d řefraḥet i bnadem nni icnan zzat i wudem nnes. \add Maca\add* i umednub ittic as ccɣeř maḥend ad iyarw u ad issmun, ḥima ad t iwc \add xenni\add* i wenni iǧan icnan zzat i wudem n AREBBI. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ. \x ◘ \xo 2:26 \xt Ayub 27:16, 17; Awřn. 28:8; Amb. 3:13\x*
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Marra ɣares tsaɛɛet nnes
\m 
\v 1 Marra ɣares řmijař nnes u aqa din \add ɛawed\add* tasaɛɛet \add ittwaggen\add* i kuř anway sadu ajenna.
\b
\m 
\v 2 Aqa din ict n tsaɛɛet n tarwa
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n řmewt,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n taẓẓut
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n weqřaɛ n min itwaẓẓun,
\m 
\v 3 ict n tsaɛɛet n tmenɣiwt
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n usgenfi,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n wehdam
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n řebni,
\m 
\v 4 ict n tsaɛɛet n imeṭṭawen
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n tḍeḥḥact,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n wecḍan
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n ccḍiḥ,
\m 
\v 5 ict n tsaɛɛet n uḥejjar n weẓru
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n wejraw n weẓru,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n udarreɛ
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n řaggʷaj x udarreɛ, \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt 1 Kur. 7:5\x*
\m 
\v 6 ict n tsaɛɛet n tarezzut
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n uweddar,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n uxemmer
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n wenḍar,
\m 
\v 7 ict n tsaɛɛet n ucarreg
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n uxeyyeḍ,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n useɣdi
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n řhard,
\m 
\v 8 ict n tsaɛɛet n tayri
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n wecrah,
\m ict n tsaɛɛet n garra
\m d ict n tsaɛɛet n řehna.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Man tizi ɣar wenni ixeddmen x min xef yarebber? \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Amb. 1:3\x*
\v 10 Necc ẓriɣ ccɣeř nni iwca AREBBI i tarwa n bnadem maḥend ad zzayes ssiḥřen ixef nsen.
\v 11 Netta igga marra d aṣebḥan di řweqt nnes. Igga uřa d řweqt n řebda deg wuř nsen, břa ma izemmar bnadem ad iḥaka di tmegga nni igga AREBBI zeg umezwaru ař aneggaru.
\v 12 Necc ufiɣ war ɣarsen iǧi min iḥřan x minni farrḥen \add iwdan\add* niɣ ad arren meẓri meřmi nitni \add ɛad\add* di tudart nsen,
\v 13 u ɛawed aqa kuř bnadem ad icc, ad isu uca ad yarr meẓri di min iṣebḥen di marra amarret nnes. Aya d ict n tarzeft n AREBBI.
\m 
\v 14 Necc ssneɣ aqa marra min ittegg AREBBI, ad yiři i řebda. War izemmar ad ɣares ittmarni walu u war zzayes ittwassenqis walu. AREBBI igga \add i-t\add* maḥend ad ggʷeden zzat i wudem nnes.
\v 15 Min iǧan, tuɣa iǧa qbeř uca min i ɣa yiřin, tuɣa iǧa \add qbeř\add*. AREBBI yarezzu x min iɛdun \add ɛad\add*.
\b
\s1 Actab n umsegged d yinni war iseggden
\m 
\v 16 Aqa ẓriɣ sadu tfuct ɛawed amcan n řḥeqq: aqa iselleṭ din řɣecc, \add uca ẓriɣ\add* uřa d amcan n tsegda: aqa \add iselleṭ\add* din řɣar.
\v 17 Necc nniɣ deg wuř inu: “AREBBI ad iḥkem amsegged d uɛeffan, maɣar dinni ict n tsaɛɛet i kuř anway u i qaɛ řxedmet.”
\v 18 Necc nniɣ deg wuř inu: “Aqa di ṭṭweɛ n tarwa n bnadem, aqa AREBBI ad ten issifef u nitni ad twařan aqa nitni am řmař, nitni s yixef nsen.”
\v 19 Maɣar x tira n tarwa n bnadem u x tira n řmař: nitni ɣarsen tira d ict. Am mammec immut wa, immut uřa d wenneɣni, marra idsen ɣarsen d twarrit n nnefs d ijj. War din iǧi řefḍeř i bnadem x řmař, maɣar marra aqa-t di řbaṭeř.
\v 20 Marra idsen gguren ɣar ijj n wemcan, marra nitni zeg ucař uca ad dd-dewřen ɣar ucař. \x ◘ \xo 3:20 \xt Amz. 3:19\x*
\v 21 Wi issnen, ma buḥbeř n tarwa n bnadem ad igeɛɛed ɣar sennej u buḥbeř n řmař ad dd-ihwa ɣar temmurt?
\v 22 Ammu i ttwařiɣ, war iǧi min iḥřan x minni ifarreḥ bnadem di tmegga nnes, maɣar man aya d tasɣart nnes, minzi man wen izemmaren ad t yarr ař ɣa iẓar min ɣa yiřin awarni as?
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Wenni iḥeṣṣaren d wenni ittwaḥṣaren
\m 
\v 1 Ẓriɣ ɛawed marra ddeǧ i ittwaggen sadu tfuct. Xzar, aqa da imeṭṭawen n yinni ittwadeǧen, \add maca\add* war ɣarsen bu umfewwej. Iffeɣ-dd lɛunf zeg ufus n yinni ten ittedǧan, \add maca\add* war ɣarsen bu umfewwej.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ṣebbḥeɣ imettinen nni immuten ɛad \add aṭṭas zeg wami\add*, zeg inni iddaren, inni ɛad iddaren.
\v 3 \add Maca\add* iḥřan xasen s tnayen idsen nni d wenni war iǧin ɛad, d wenni war iẓrin \add ɛad\add* timegga tiɛeffanin nni ittwaggent sadu tfuct.
\m 
\v 4 Uca necc ẓriɣ marra amarret d marra tizemmar di řxedmet, aqa-t mɣir d amɛanad n ijj ak-d wenneɣni. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\v 5 Abuhaři iḍfes ifassen nnes uca ittett aysum \add n ixef\add* nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:5 \xt Awřn. 6:10; 24:33\x*
\v 6 Iḥřa ijj n wuru \add n ufus\add* iccur s řhudnet uřa tnayen n ifassen ccuren s umarret d weḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\b
\s1 Amarret n wenni weḥḥdes
\m 
\v 7 Ɛawed ẓriɣ \add ca\add* min iǧan di řbaṭeř sadu tfuct.
\v 8 Aqa \add din\add* ijjen \add aqa t ḥafi\add* u war din wenni d wiss tnayen i ibedden ɣares. Uřa war ɣares iǧi uḥenjir u war ɣares umas. War iǧi uneggar ɣar marra amarret nnes, uřa war tᵉttyiwinent tiṭṭawin nnes zeg wagřa. “I umi tteggeɣ tamara u ssekkiɣ tt di řeɛmar inu zi tcuni?” Uřa d man aya di řbaṭeř d ijj n ccɣeř iwɛar i yeǧa.
\v 9 Tnayen ḥsen zeg ijjen waha, maɣar nitni ɣarsen řmunet d lemliḥ deg umarret nsen.
\v 10 Maɣar mařa nitni wḍan, ad issnekkar ijjen zeg umɛacar nnes ɛawed. \add Maca\add* axeyyeb i wenni iǧan weḥḥdes mařa netta iwḍa, minzi war din ittiři ḥed, maḥend ad t issnekkar ad ibedd.
\v 11 Ɛawed mařa tnayen ṭṭsen munen, ad ɣarsen yiři řeḥmu, \add maca\add* mammec ɣa igg ijjen weḥḥdes ad iḥma?
\v 12 Mařa din ijjen yarna x ijjen i iǧan weḥḥdes, \add maca\add* tnayen ad ɣares bedden \add jmiɛ\add*. Ijj n wesɣun imuden x třata war iqeṭṭu deɣya.
\b
\s1 Ajeǧid aḥenjir d umiɣis
\m 
\v 13 Iḥra ijj n uḥudri d amezřuḍ d amiɣis zeg ijj n ujeǧid iwsar d abuhaři i war ifehhmen ɛad i weɛřam.
\v 14 Maɣar ad dd-iffeɣ zi řeḥbes maḥend ad idweř d ajeǧid waxxa netta ittwaxřeq-dd d amezřuḍ di tgeldit nnes.
\v 15 Necc ẓriɣ marra inni iddaren i igguren sadu tfuct, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d uḥudri, wenni d wiss tnayen nni i ɣa ibedden deg wemcan nnes.
\v 16 War din aneggar ɣar řgens nni am ikmeř nni zi izwar netta \add am yixef\add*. \add Waxxa amenni\add* uřa d inni dd ɣa yasen awarni as, war zzayes farrḥen. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\b
\s1 X řwuɛud i Arebbi
\m 
\v 17 Ḥḍa aṣurif nnec mařa cek teggured ɣar Taddart n AREBBI. Aqarreb ḥima ad tesḥessed, ḥsen zeg uwehheb n tɣarṣt s \add ufus n\add* ibuhařiyyen, maɣar nitni war ssinen aqa nitni tteggen tuɛeffna.
\b
\b
\c 5
\m 
\v 1 War tqeǧiq s uqemmum nnec u ḥḍa aqa uř nnec war ittemḥizwar ad inṭeq awař zzat i AREBBI. Maɣar AREBBI deg ujenna, \add maca\add* cek di temmurt. X uya ejj ad iřin wawařen nnec udrusen.
\v 2 Maɣar am tarjit tᵉttas-dd s waṭṭas n řehhu, ammu uřa d řhard n ubuhaři s waṭṭas n wawařen.
\m 
\v 3 Mařa cek teggid i AREBBI ict n tjaǧit, war ttraja ca \add xenni\add* maḥend ad tt tkemmřed, maɣar war d as tteɛjiben ibuhařiyyen. Min twaɛded, ittxeṣṣa ad t ttkemmřed. \x ◘ \xo 5:3 \xt Řxř. 30:3; Aɛwd. 23:20\x*
\v 4 Ihřa mařa war twaɛded x mařa cek twaɛded, \add maca\add* war tkemmřed. \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Aɛwd. 23:20, 21\x*
\v 5 War ttejji aqa aqemmum nnec ad yarr arrimet nnec ad texḍa u war teqqar zzat i wudem n lmalak, aqa man aya d aweddar waha. Mayemmi ɣa iffugem AREBBI x min teqqared u ad yareddeǧ řxedmet n ifassen nnec?
\v 6 Maɣar deg waṭṭas n tirja, aqa daysent min iǧan di řbaṭeř, ammu uřa deg waṭṭas n wawařen. S uya: Ggʷed AREBBI!\x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Awřn. 10:19\x*
\b
\s1 Řeḥṣaret d usfarɣ n řḥeqq
\m 
\v 7 Mařa cek tḥekkared řeḥṣaret n imezřaḍ uřa d amnaɛ n řḥeqq d tsegda di lɛamala, war ttarjif ca aqa \add man aya\add* yusa-dd \add asen\add* s řxaḍar, maɣar x yijj n umeqqran aqa din wenni d ameqqran \add xas\add* uca xasen bedden inni d imeqqranen \add ɛad\add*.
\v 8 Ijj n ujeǧid ittceṭṭaren i temmurt \add n tfeǧaḥt\add*, aqa netta d řefḍeř i temmurt di marra iɣezdisen.
\b
\s1 Ad ifna wagřa d bnadem
\m 
\v 9 Wenni ittexsen tmenyat, war ittjiwin ɛemmarṣ tmenyat, u wenni ittexsen agřa, ɛemmarṣ \add war ittjiwin\add* řmunet \add nnes\add*. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř.
\m 
\v 10 Mani ittmarni wagřa, ammu ttmarnin uřa d inni t i ɣa iccen. Man řefḍeř i ɣa iqqimen i aytbab nnes mɣir tiṭṭawin nsen zemmarent ad xzarent \add aya\add*?
\v 11 Iḍeṣ n uxeddam d miẓid, ma netta ɣares drus niɣ aṭṭas n macca, \add maca\add* i bu-wagřa afeyyeḍ nnes war t ittejji ad iṭṭeṣ.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Aqa din ijj n řɣar i ẓriɣ sadu tfuct, \add ijj n řɣar\add* ittegg am řehřac: agřa ittɛess xas bab nnes i druct i ixef nnes.
\v 13 Ifna \add zeɛma\add* wagřa nnes s ict n temsart d taɛeffant uca netta tuɣa yejj-dd mmis, \add xenni\add* war ɣares iqqim walu \add ɛad\add* deg ufus nnes.
\v 14 Am mammec dd-iffeɣ netta zeg uɛeddis n yemmas, \add ammu i ɣa\add* iɛqeb d aɛaryan. Ad yuyur am mammec i dd-yusa. S \add marra\add* amarret nnes i zi imarret, war \add izemmar\add* ad \add kides\add* iksi uřa d ict řḥajjet deg ufus nnes. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Izhd. 49:18\x*
\v 15 Uřa d ta d ict n tmesřact d taɛeffant: nican mammec i dd-yusa netta, ad yuyur. Man řefḍeř nnes \add xenni\add* i wenni imarrten i usemmiḍ \add waha\add*?
\v 16 Ɛawed ittɣima ittett di taǧest marra ussan nnes am kemřen. Ittwamarret \add s\add* řeḥřac nnes d uduqqez nnes n weɣḍab.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Xzar, min ttwařiɣ d man aya: aqa d lemliḥ u icna aqa \add ijj\add* ad icc, ad isu u ad iẓar marra řxar i marra amarret nnes i umi ittmarrat \add bnadem\add* sadu tafuct di řqedd n wussan n tudart i d as dd-yarzef AREBBI, maɣar ta d tasɣart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Amb. 2:10, 24; 3:12, 22; 9:7; 11:9\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ɛawed kuř bnadem i umi iwca AREBBI agřa d txubay u i umi iwca tizemmar maḥend ad zzayes icc u ad zzayes yarbu tasɣart nnes u ad zzayes ifarḥ ɣar umarret nnes, aqa-tt d tarzeft n AREBBI.
\v 19 Maɣar netta war ittidar \add ɛad\add* aṭṭas deg wussan n tudart nnes, minzi AREBBI isřa as umi \add d as\add* iwca řefraḥet deg wuř nnes.
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Agřa nni zzaysen bab nsen war dd-yarr meẓri
\m 
\v 1 Aqa din ijj n řɣar nni ẓriɣ sadu tfuct nni imsaren aṭṭas jar iwdan:
\v 2 ijjen yarzef as AREBBI agřa d txubay d ccan. Aqa war ittxeṣṣi walu i řeɛmar nnes zi marra min dayes d meẓri, \add maca\add* AREBBI war t ijji ad zzayes icc, \add maɣar\add* ijj n ubarrani ad t icc. Aqa uřa d man aya di řbaṭeř d ijj n řɣar d aɛeffan.
\m 
\v 3 Mařa ijj n weryaz yejj-dd mya n iḥenjiren u iddar aṭṭas n iseggʷusa, ařami dewřen wussan n tudart nnes deg waṭṭas, \add maca\add* řeɛmar nnes war ijjiwen ca s řxar u war ittwif wenḍeř i netta, necc ad iniɣ: ijj n weɣray icna as x netta.
\v 4 Maɣar yusa-dd di řbaṭeř uca iffeɣ di taǧest u s taǧest ittwařeḥḥef isem nnes.
\v 5 Netta ɛawed war iẓri tafuct u war tt issin. \add Ammu\add* ɣar \add weɣray-a\add* řhudnet ktar x \add weryaz\add* nni, \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Ayub 3:16; Izhd. 58:9\x*
\v 6 waxxa netta iddar ařfayen n iseggʷusa, \add maca\add* břa ma ad iẓar řxar! Ma war igguren kuř ijj ɣar wemcan d ijj?
\m 
\v 7 Marra amarret n bnadem i uqemmum nnes, waxxa amenni ɛemmarṣ war ittccuri řeɛmar nnes.
\v 8 Maɣar man řefḍeř i umiɣis x ubuhaři? \add Man řefḍeř i\add* umezřuḍ nni issnen ad yuyur qibač i yinni iddaren?
\v 9 Iḥřa ad teẓrid min iǧan zzat i tiṭṭawin x wetlaɛ n řeɛmar. Uřa d man aya di řbaṭeř d weḍfar n usemmiḍ.
\m 
\v 10 Min ma iǧa ca n ijjen, aqa isem nnes ittwařaɣa qbeř, u tuɣa ittwassen min ɣa yiři bnadem: netta war izemmar ad imcubbec ak-d Wenni xas ijehden. \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt Ica. 45:9; Rum. 9:20. \x*
\v 11 Maɣar aqa din aṭṭas n wawařen nni yarennyen di min iǧan di řbaṭeř. Man řefḍeř \add n uya\add* i bnadem?
\v 12 Maɣar wi izemmaren ad issen min iḥřan i bnadem di tudart \add nnes\add* di řweqt n řqedd n wussan n tudart \add nnes\add* ifennan nni issɛeddu am tiři? Maɣar wi izemmaren ad isscen i bnadem min ɣa imsaren awarni as sadu tfuct? \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt Amb. 8:7; Izhd. 144:4; Yaɛ. 4:13, 14\x*
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Taddart n řefraḥet d taddart n wecḍan
\m 
\v 1 Isem iṣbeḥ iḥřa x zzect iṣebḥen, ass n řmewt \add iḥřa\add* x wass n tarwa. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt Awřn. 22:1\x*
\v 2 Teḥřa twaḥit ɣar taddart n wecḍan x twaḥit ɣar taddart \add mani ttqeddamen\add* ict n zzardet, \add minzi din\add* iǧa qeṭṭu n bnadem marra, u wenni iddaren ittegg i-tt deg wuř nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Yḥ. 11:31\x*
\v 3 Iḥřa wecḍan x tdeḥḥact, maɣar s ijj n uɣembub iceḍnen iddakkʷař wuř ḥsen.
\v 4 Uř n imiɣisen \add aqa-t\add* di taddart n wecḍan, \add maca\add* uř n ibuhařiyyen \add aqa-t\add* di taddart n řefraḥet.
\m 
\v 5 Iḥřa ad tesřed ɣar uwebbex zeg imiɣisen x wesḥessi i yezři n ibuhařiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Awřn. 13:18; 15:31, 32\x*
\v 6 Maɣar am utartek n isennanen sadu umeqraj, ammu i tegga tḍeḥḥact n ubuhaři. Uřa d man aya aqa-t di řbaṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Izhd. 58:10\x*
\b
\s1 Iɛřamen
\m 
\v 7 Maɣar řeḥṣaret ad tessbuhři amiɣis, u tarzeft \add n arrecwet\add* tessexsara uř.
\m 
\v 8 Aneggaru n tmesřact teḥřa x umezwaru nnes. Wenni ɣar iǧa ttasiɛ n řxaḍar aṭṭas iḥřa x umɛeffar.
\m 
\v 9 War sexxeḍ deɣya di buḥbeř nnec, maɣar deg weḥsin n ibuhařiyyen izeddeɣ uxeyyeq. \f ◼ \fr 7:9 \fk aḥsin\ft - niɣ ‘abeḥrur’.\f*
\m 
\v 10 War teqqar: “Min tuɣa \add din\add*, aqa ussan n zic iḥřan x mammec ǧan wussan-a?” Maɣar aseqsi-ya war \add izemmar ad iffeɣ\add* zi tiɣit.
\m 
\v 11 Tiɣit i dd-ittasen ak-d tesɣart tecna, u \add tiɣit\add* aqa d řefḍeř i yinni ittwařan tafuct.
\m 
\v 12 Maɣar am mammec tiɣit teǧa d taseddart \add i useřqi\add*, \add ammu\add* uřa d tmenyat aqa atent d taseddart \add i useřqi\add*. Řefḍeř n tussna aqa tiɣit tᵉttic tudart i aytbab nnes.
\m 
\v 13 Xzar min igga AREBBI, maɣar wi izemmaren ad iseggem min issfarɣ Netta?
\m 
\v 14 Arr meẓri s řxar deg wass n wefřaḥ, \add maca\add* deg wass n arẓiyyet, xzar \add xenni\add*, maɣar AREBBI igga wa uřa d ta, ḥima bnadem war izemmar ad yaf awarni as walu. \f ◼ \fr 7:14 \fk awarni as\ft - man aya ixs ad yini ‘awarni i řmewt nnes’.\f*
\b
\s1 Uyur x webrid n řwest
\m 
\v 15 Marra aya i ẓriɣ deg wussan \add n tudart inu\add* ifennan. Aqa din amsegged nni ittwahellken di tsegda nnes uca aqa din aɛeffan nni isszuggarten \add ussan nnes\add* di marra tuɛeffna nnes.
\v 16 War ttegg ixef nnec d amsegged aṭṭas, u war ttegg ixef nnec d amiɣis aṭṭas. Mayemmi ɣa tareddǧed ixef nnec?
\v 17 War ttiři d aɛeffan aṭṭas u war ttiři ɛawed d abuhaři aṭṭas. Mayemmi ɣa temmted mařa war dd-yiwiḍ ɛad řmijař nnec?
\v 18 Mliḥ mařa cek tcebbared di ta, \add am\add* war yarexxu ufus nnec di tin, maɣar wenni itteggʷeden AREBBI, ad ittwafekk zi marra aya.
\m 
\v 19 Tiɣit tessejhed amiɣis \add x\add* ɛecra n ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa nni iǧan deg ict n tendint.
\m 
\v 20 Wah nican, war iǧi uřa d ijj n bnadem d amsegged x temmurt, \add uřa d ijj\add* ittegg řxar u war ixeṭṭi ca. \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt 1 Ij. 8:46, 47; 2 Im. 6:36; Awřn. 20:9; 1 Yḥ. 1:8; Rum. 3:10-12\x*
\m 
\v 21 War ttic taynit nnec i marra awařen nni qqaren iwdan, ḥima ɛemmarṣ war tᵉttesřid aqa amsexxar nnec ad cek inɛeř.
\v 22 Maɣar uř nnec yuca aṭṭas n twařawin, aqa uřa d cek tneɛřed inneɣni.
\b
\s1 Tarezzut d tidett tiwi-dd bnadem ɣar Arebbi
\m 
\v 23 Marra aya beqqceɣ t s tiɣit. Necc nniɣ: “Xseɣ ad kesbeɣ tiɣit!”, \add maca\add* tiɣit teqqim ayi ɣar řaggʷaj.
\v 24 \add Maɣar\add* min iggʷejen d min yuǧɣen, \add wah,\add* yuǧɣen, man wen izemmaren ad t yaf?
\v 25 Nnqeřbeɣ, uřa d uř inu \add akidi\add*, maḥend ad afeɣ tussna, maḥend ad beqqceɣ, ad arzuɣ tiɣit d wenway \add i dayes\add*, maḥend ad ssneɣ \add s tidett\add* aqa řɣar d taɣyuři u taɣyuři \add dayes\add* aṭemmes aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 7:25 \xt Amb. 1:17; 2:12\x*
\m 
\v 26 Ufiɣ min iǧan d amerzag x řmewt: tamɣart \add tenni iǧan am\add* traccawin u uř nnes \add amecnaw\add* řefxux \add ineqqen\add* u ifassen nnes \add amecnaw\add* iceddiyyen. Wenni yarḍan zzat i wudem n AREBBI, izemmar ad zzayes infekk, \add maca\add* amednub ad zzayes imxumber. \x ◘ \xo 7:26 \xt Awřn. 5:3; 6:24-35; 7:6-27; 22:14\x*
\m 
\v 27 Xzar, aya i ufiɣ, iqqar Umbarreḥ, \add umi arenyeɣ\add* ict \add n řḥajjet\add* i yicten \add nneɣni\add* maḥend \add ammu i\add* ɣa yafeɣ řḥasuř \add nnes\add*:
\v 28 min tuɣa yarezzu řeɛmar inu ɛad, \add maca\add* war t ufiɣ. \add Wah\add* ufiɣ ijj n weryaz deg wařef, \add maca\add* ict n temɣart war tt ufiɣ jar marra yina.
\v 29 Xzar, ict waha i ufiɣ, aqa AREBBI igga bnadem nican, \add maca\add* nitni arzun deg waṭṭas n yebriden iḥraymeyyen.
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Tiɣit teṭṭaɛ
\m 
\v 1 Wi iǧan am umiɣis u wi issnen ad ifekk ict n tmesřact? Tiɣit n bnadem tᵉttarra aɣembub nnes ittnewwar uca tbeddeř \add tifras\add* n řeqseḥ n uɣembub nnes.
\v 2 Necc \add qqareɣ\add*: “Ḥḍa aḍebbar n ujeǧid!” u \add man aya\add* di ssibbet n tjaǧit n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Awřn. 24:21\x*
\v 3 War ttiggʷij s tazřa x wudem nnes, war ttegg azeǧif nnec di tmesřact taɛeffant, maɣar netta igga marra min xef yarḍa.
\v 4 Awař n ujeǧid dayes ṣṣulṭa temɣar. Man wen izemmaren ad as yini: “Min tᵉttegged cek?”
\m 
\v 5 Wenni iḥeṭṭan tawṣeyyet, war t iřeqqef \add walu n\add* min iǧan d aɛeffan. Uř n umiɣis issen řḥař d řḥukm. \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Rum. 13:3\x*
\v 6 Maɣar i kuř anway ijj n řḥař d ijj n řḥukm, maɣar tuɛeffna n bnadem tessedqař i-t.
\m 
\v 7 Maɣar netta war issin min ɣa imsaren, maɣar man wen i d as t i ɣa isscnen mammec ɣa yiři aya? \x ◘ \xo 8:7 \xt Amb. 6:12\x*
\v 8 War \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ijj n bnadem izemmar x usuḍi n usemmiḍ ařami izemmar ad xas ibelleɛ. War \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ijj ɣares ṣṣulṭa x wass n řmewt, u war \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ijj izemmar ad iksi ttesriḥ deg umenɣi, u tuɛeffna war tejji ad nejmen aytbab nnes. \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt Ayub 14:5; Izhd. 39:6\x*
\v 9 Marra aya ẓriɣ t, umi ssenqeřbeɣ uř inu ɣar marra min ittwaggen sadu tfuct, di řweqt řami iṣelleṭ bnadem x bnadem nneɣni i druct nnes.
\b
\s1 Tasegda n Arebbi aqa-tt tnuffar
\m 
\v 10 Ammu i ẓriɣ iɛeffanen nni tuɣa ittwaneḍřen, udfen \add ɣar wenḍeř\add*, \add umi\add* yinni iggin min iǧan nican ffɣen zeg wemcan amqeddas, ttwattun di tendint. Uřa d man aya di řbaṭeř.
\v 11 Maɣar řḥukm x tɛeffant war ittwagg deɣya, x uya iccur wuř n tarwa n bnadem maḥend ad ggen min iǧan d aɛeffan.
\v 12 Waxxa amednub ittegg taɛeffant mya n twařawin u iddar aṭṭas, waxxa amenni ssneɣ aqa inni itteggʷeden AREBBI ad feřḥen, inni zzayes itteggʷeden. \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Izhd. 37:9, 10, 11, 12, 18, 19, 20; Awřn. 1:33; Ica. 3:10\x*
\v 13 Aɛeffan \add maca\add* war ittiři mliḥ u war ɣares tᵉttiři tudart d tazirart. Netta ad yiři am tiři, maɣar war itteggʷed AREBBI.
\m 
\v 14 Aqa din ca min ittwaggen x temmurt nni iǧan di řbaṭeř: aqa din imseggaden ittemmsar asen axmi tteggen am yiɛeffanen, u aqa din iɛeffanen ittemsar asen axmi tteggen tasegda. Necc nniɣ: uřa d man aya di řbaṭeř.
\v 15 S uyenni i ttṣebbaḥeɣ řefraḥet, maɣar war din iǧi i bnadem min iǧan ḥsen \add di tudart nnes\add* sadu tfuct mɣir mařa netta ittett, isess u ifarreḥ. Iři aya ad t iɛacar deg umarret nnes di marra ussan n tudart nnes i d as yarzef AREBBI sadu tfuct. \x ◘ \xo 8:15 \xt Amb. 2:24; 3:12, 22; 5:18; 9:7\x*
\m 
\v 16 Umi tuɣa ggiɣ uř inu maḥend ad ssneɣ tiɣit u maḥend ad xzareɣ man tasebbabt i igguren x temmurt - maɣar am s wass am s ǧiřet bnadem war ittic ca arraḥet i tiṭṭawin nnes -
\v 17 ẓriɣ marra min igga AREBBI, aqa bnadem war izemmar ad yaf min ittwaggen, \add ixs ad yini\add* min ittwaggen sadu tfuct. Maɣar mammec i ɣa imarret bnadem am yarezzu, war ittif walu. Waxxa amiɣis ad yini belli netta issen, netta war izemmar maca ad t yaf.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Bnadem war izemmar ad iḥkem tasɣart nnes
\m 
\v 1 Maɣar necc ggiɣ marra aya ɣar wuř inu, maḥend ad arzuɣ di marra aya, aqa imseggaden d imiɣisen d tmegga nsen deg ufus n AREBBI. Tayri d wecrah war ten issin bnadem, aqa marra iǧa zzates.
\v 2 Marra \add iǧa\add* am mammec \add iǧa\add* ɣar marra: tira d ict třeqqef amsegged d uɛeffan, am uṣebḥan d umezdag am umexmuj, wenni iqeddmen taɣarṣt d wenni war iqeddmen taɣarṣt, aṣebḥan d umednub, wenni ittjjaǧan d wenni itteggʷeden maḥend ad ijjaǧ. \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Izhd. 73:12, 13\x*
\v 3 Man aya d ijj n řɣar ɣar marra min imsaren sadu tfuct, aqa marra \add iwdan\add* iřqef i-ten tira d ict, uca uřa uř n tarwa n bnadem iccur s řɣar, u aqa din aṭemmes deg wuř nsen di řweqt n tudart nsen, u awarni i uya \add ad uyuren nitni\add* ɣar imettinen.
\v 4 Maɣar i wenni iqqnen i marra inni iddaren aqa din asitem, minzi řḥař i weqzin iddaren ḥsen zi \add řḥař\add* i weyrad immuten.
\v 5 Maɣar inni iddaren ssnen, aqa nitni ad mmten, \add maca\add* imettan war ssinen walu qaɛ. Nitni war ttᵉṭṭfen walu zi řmunet, maɣar řidaret xafsen tᵉttwattu.
\v 6 Aqa tayri nsen d wecrah nsen d tusmi nsen fnan. I řebda war ɣarsen bu tesɣart ɛad di marra min ittemsaren sadu tfuct.
\m 
\v 7 Uyur \add xenni\add*, iwa ecc s řefraḥet aɣrum nnec, su s wuř ifarḥen binu nnec, maɣar iɛjeb as i AREBBI timegga nnec aṭṭas zeg wami.
\v 8 Ejj ad yiři arruḍ nnec d acemřař řebda u ɛemmarṣ war ittxeṣṣi zzect x uzeǧif nnec.
\v 9 Barreɛ x tudart ak-d temɣart nni tᵉttexsed, marra ussan n tudart nnec ifennan nni d as iwca AREBBI sadu tfuct, mařa ussan n lḥaḍar nnec ifennan danita, maɣar ta d tasɣart nnec di tudart-a u ɣar umarret i zi tmarrted sadu tfuct.
\v 10 Marra min ɣa yaf ufus nnec maḥend ad t yegg, egg i-t ɛlaḥsab jjehd nnec, maɣar war iǧi di řaxart mani ɣa tuyured min ɣa tegged, niɣ axarreṣ niɣ tussna uřa d tiɣit.
\m 
\v 11 Ɛawed ẓriɣ sadu tfuct aqa ayt n bu-tazřa war ɣeǧben \add řebda\add* di ḥamat, niɣ ayt n bu-teɣruḍt \add řebda\add* deg umenɣi, u imiɣisen war ɣarsen iǧi weɣrum \add řebda\add* u yinni s řeɛqeř war ɣarsen iǧi wagřa \add řebda\add*, uřa d inni s řefhamet war ɣarsen iǧi arḍa \add řebda\add*, maɣar řḥař d tira řeqqfen uřa d marra nitni.
\v 12 Maɣar bnadem war issin řmijař nnes, am yiseřman inḥeṣren di tracca n arẓiyyet, u am yijḍaḍ innḥeṣren di řfex. Ammu uřa d tarwa n bnadem ttwaṭṭfen di řfex deg ict n řweqt d taɛeffant, xmi xasen dd-tweṭṭa \add tracca\add* deɣya.
\b
\s1 Tiɣit war ɣares bu uweqqar
\m 
\v 13 Uřa d man aya bdiɣ ad dayes ẓriɣ tiɣit sadu tfuct, tusa ayi-dd d tameqqrant aṭṭas.
\v 14 Tuɣa din ict n tendint d tameẓyant dayes drus n yewdan \add waha\add*. Iffeɣ xas ijj n ujeǧid d ameqqran, iḥewwes i-tt, u issbedd xas lbarajat timeqqranin.
\v 15 Ittwaff dayes ijj n weryaz d amezřuḍ d amiɣis wenni ifekken tandint s tiɣit nnes, \add maca\add* uřa d ijj n bnadem iɛqeř \add ɛad ɛemmarṣ\add* x weryaz nni.
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ necc: “Tiɣit teḥřa x jjhed!”, waxxa tᵉttwasseḥqar tiɣit n umezřuḍ u awařen nnes war tᵉttwasřen. \x ◘ \xo 9:16 \xt Awřn. 21:22; 24:5; Amb. 7:19\x*
\m 
\v 17 Awařen n imiɣisen nni ɣar ttesřan \add iwdan\add* di řhudnet, ḥsen zeg uɣuyyi n řḥakem jar ibuhařiyyen.
\v 18 Tiɣit teḥřa x řesnaḥ n umenɣi, \add maca\add* ijj n umednub \add waha\add* iheddem aṭṭas.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Aqarri n tubbuheřya
\m 
\v 1 Izan ineqqen ttarran zzect n wedhan n uɛeṭṭar ad tarṣuḍ u ad tesmem. Drus n tubbuheřya twezzen aṭṭas x tiɣit d ccan.
\v 2 Uř n umiɣis aqa-t \add i netta\add* afus nnes afusi, \add maca\add* uř n ubuhaři \add i wanita\add* afus nnes azeřmaḍ.
\v 3 Uřa deg webrid min xef iggur ubuhaři, uř nnes war imtin, iqqar i marra aqa netta d abuhaři.
\v 4 Mařa xak ixeyyeq buḥbeř n bu-jjehd, war tteggʷij x wemcan nnec, maɣar man aya d ddwa, yaressa ddnub imeqqranen.
\m 
\v 5 Aqa din ijj n řɣar nneɣni nni ẓriɣ sadu tfuct, aqa-t d ijj n uweddar i dd-iffɣen zeg ijj n bu-ṣṣulṭa:
\v 6 asgeɛɛad aṭṭas n tubbuheřya, \add am\add* ttɣiman ayt n bu-wagřa swadday.
\v 7 Necc ẓriɣ imsexxaren nyin x yeysan uřa d řḥukkam nni igguren am yimsexxaren \add x iḍaren nsen\add* x temmurt.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Wenni itteqqazen aḥfur, ad dayes iwḍa \add s yixef nnes\add*, wenni issnuqqben řḥiḍ, izemmar ad as iqqes ufiɣar. \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt Awřn. 26:27\x*
\m 
\v 9 Wenni ikksen iẓra, ad \add zzaysen\add* iyzem \add ixef nnes\add*, wenni ittfettqen akeccuḍ, ad yiři di lxaṭar.
\m 
\v 10 Mařa uzzař \add n ccaqur\add* idweř iḥfa u \add bab nnes\add* war t isseqḍeɛ, xenni ittxeṣṣa as jjhed ktar, \add maca\add* tiɣit tecna aṭṭas ḥima ad ifřeḥ bnadem.
\v 11 Mařa izɛef ufiɣar qbeř aɛezzem, war din řefḍeř i uɛezzam.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Awařen zeg uqemmum n umiɣis daysen arḍa, \add maca\add* iyencicen n ubuhaři ṣarḍen t simant nnes.
\v 13 Beddu n wawařen zeg uqemmum nnes d tubbuheřya u aneggaru n min dd-iffɣen zeg uqemmum nnes d aṭemmes aɛeffan.
\v 14 Abuhaři ittkettar řhard aṭṭas, maca bnadem war issin min ɣa imsaren, u min ɣa imsaren awarni as, wi d as t i ɣa iɛawden?
\v 15 Amarret n ibuhařiyyen ittarra i-ten uḥřen, maɣar nitni war ssinen mammec ɣa yuyuren ɣar tendint.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Uct xam, \add a\add* tammurt, mařa ajeǧid nnem d aḥenjir \add ɛad\add*, u řḥukkam nnem ɣar teffut ttᵉtten! \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Ica. 3:3, 4; Ḥuc. 13:11; Ɛam. 6:4\x*
\v 17 Sseɛd nnem, \add a\add* tammurt, mařa ajeǧid nnem d mmis n tarwa n taṣiřet, u řḥukkam nnem ttᵉtten ɣar řweqt ittwaggen, maḥend ad ttwameḥden, war iǧi maḥend ad skaren.
\m 
\v 18 S řeɛgez i hekkwant tiḥenya u s ifassen yarehfen ad tudum taddart.
\v 19 \add Bnadem\add* ittegg aɣrum maḥend ad iḍḥec, binu issfarraḥ inni iddaren u tmenyat neffɛent i marra min iǧan.
\m 
\v 20 War neɛɛeř ajeǧid \add ɛad\add* di řbař nnec, deg wexxam n yiḍeṣ war neɛɛeř bu-wagřa, maɣar ijḍaḍ n ujenna zemmaren ad ssuyuren řḥess \add n wawařen nnec\add* u \add ammu marra\add* wi ɣar ǧan wafriwen izemmar ad isseɛdu awař. \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Uf. 22:28\x*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Ixarriṣen war zemmaren ad beḍřen řxedmet
\m 
\v 1 Sekk aɣrum nnec tiwa i waman, maɣar awarni i aṭṭas n wussan ad t tafed \add ɛawed\add*.
\v 2 Bḍa t di sebɛa niɣ ɛad di tmenya, maɣar cek war tessined man řɣar i ɣa yiřin di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt 2 Kur. 9:10\x*
\m 
\v 3 Mařa ccuren iseynuten, ttzeǧaɛen anẓar x temmurt. Ma tacejjart tewḍa ɣar ljanub niɣ ɣar ccamal, deg wemcan mani tewḍa, tᵉttɣima din \add tezzeř\add*. \f ◼ \fr 11:3 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\m 
\v 4 Wenni ixezzaren řebda ɣar usemmiḍ, war ittiwiḍ ad izarɛ, wenni iḥeṭṭan řebda iseynuten, war ittiwiḍ ad imjar.
\m 
\v 5 Am mammec cek war tessined abrid n usemmiḍ, ammu \add i war tessined uřa\add* mammec ttwaggen iɣsan deg uɛeddis n temɣart s ddeyset. Ammu i war tessined uřa d tmegga n AREBBI wenni itteggen marra \add min iǧan\add*. \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Yḥ. 3:8\x*
\v 6 Zarɛ zzariɛet nnec ɣar tuffut u war ttekkes afus nnec ɣar tmeddit, maɣar cek war tessined min i ɣa ifřeḥ, ta niɣ ta, niɣ ɛad s tnayen idsent ad iřint ṣebḥent.
\b
\s1 Xarriṣ di temẓi nnek di řḥukm n Arebbi
\m 
\v 7 Tafawt d tmiẓidt uca mliḥ i tiṭṭawin ad ẓarent tfuct.
\v 8 Wah, mařa aryaz iddar aṭṭas n iseggʷusa, ejj i-t ad ifarḥ di marra \add iseggʷusa nni\add*, u ejj i-t ad iɛqeř \add ɛawed\add*, aqa ussan ibarcanen ad iřin deg waṭṭas. Marra min i d ɣa yasen \add ɛad\add*, aqa-t di řbaṭeř.
\m 
\v 9 Farḥ, \add a cek\add* aḥudri, di temẓi nnec, sfarḥ uř nnec deg wussan n temẓi nnec. Uyur deg ibriden n wuř nnec u di min ttwařant tiṭṭawin nnec, maca ssen aqa SIDI ad cek issekk x marra aya i ccreɛ.
\v 10 Siggʷej řhemm x wuř nnec u sḥeyyed řɣar x arrimet nnec, maɣar temẓi d řweqt s ucuwwaf abarcan \add n temẓi\add* aqa aten di řbaṭeř.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Temẓi d tawessart
\m 
\v 1 Idar Wenni cek dd-ixeřqen deg wussan n temẓi nnec, \bd qbeř\bd* i dd ɣa yawḍen wussan n řɣar i zi ɣa tinid: “War daysen ufiɣ řefraḥet!”,
\v 2 \bd qbeř\bd* ad tᵉttwabarcen tfuct d tfawt d tziri d itran uca ad dd-ɛeqben iseynuten awarni i wenẓar,
\v 3 ɣar wass min di iɛessasen n taddart ad arjijen, iryazen ijehden ad qewsen, tinni iḥarryen tasirt ad ssbeddent \add tawwuri nsent\add*, minzi nitenti qqiment drus idsent, uca \add timɣarin\add* nni dd-issajjan zi řkwazi, ad ttwařeḥḥfent s taǧest,
\v 4 u tnayen n tewwura ɣar zzenqqet ad ttwabellɛent, xmi ddriz n tsirt ad isseɣd uca řḥess n ujḍiḍ ad t issiggwed deg yiḍes u marra yessis n uɣennij ad dewřent qewsent,
\v 5 u \add bnadem\add* ad iggʷed zi marra min iǧan yuɛřan, uca ad din iřint \add ɛřam kuř řeḥwayej\add* inexřiɛen deg webrid, u tacejjart n ǧewz ad tnewwar u aburxes ad idweř d tamara u tanewwact n ‘ukebbas’ war d as dd-yusi ɛad ɣar řbař - maɣar bnadem iggur ɣar taddart nnes n řebda u inni iceṭṭnen ad raḥen ad dd-tasen deg ibriden - \f ◼ \fr 12:5 \fk tanewwact n ‘ukebbas’\ft - isem-a n tnewwact tanita s tutlayt n Tlatinit: ‘capparis’. S Teɛrabt ‘الكَبَر’.\f*
\m 
\v 6 \bd qbeř\bd* i ɣa tᵉttwarxu tesɣunt n nnuqart, ad tᵉttwarẓ ṭṭawyyet n wureɣ, ad innefrar weqbuc ɣar tařa uca ad teqḍu tjarrart deg wanu,
\v 7 uca ucař ad dd-iɛqeb ɣar temmurt am mammec t-tuɣa, u buḥbeř ad dd-iɛqeb ɣar AREBBI, wenni t iwcin. \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt Amz. 2:7; 3:19; Řxř. 16:22\x*
\b
\s1 Awař aneggaru
\m 
\v 8 D ibeṭṭařen qaɛ, iqqar Umbarreḥ, aqa kuřci di řbaṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Izhd. 62:10; 144:4; Amb. 1:2\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 Sennej i uya, minzi Ambarreḥ tuɣa-t d amiɣis, isseřmed ɛawed tussna i řgens, tuɣa ittbařu, ittbeqqac mliḥ, uca iɛdeř aṭṭas n wawařen iweznen. \x ◘ \xo 12:9 \xt 1 Ij. 5:26\x*
\v 10 Yarzu Umbarreḥ maḥend ad yaf awařen iɛedřen, u min yura, aqa-t nican, awařen n tidett.
\v 11 Awařen n imiɣisen am yisennanen u amecnaw imesmiren ittwassidfen, i zzaysen i-dd-ttasent aṭṭas n tmesřayin, aqa-ten mmewcen zeg uyenni n Umeksaw. \f ◼ \fr 12:11 \fk ameksaw\ft - niɣ ‘aniči’.\f*
\m 
\v 12 Sennej i marra aya, \add a\add* mmi, ḥḍa ixef nnec: war din aqeṭṭu n tira n waṭṭas n idlisen u aṭṭas n tɣuri tessaḥař arrimet.
\m 
\v 13 Awař aneggaru n marra min tesřid, aqa t d wa: “Ggʷed AREBBI u ḥḍa tiweṣṣa nnes!”, maɣar man aya \add i yurin\add* i kuř ijj n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Aɛwd. 6:2; 10:12; Awřn. 3:7\x*
\v 14 Maɣar SIDI ad yawi kuř tameggit zzat i taddart n ccreɛ x marra min innuffaren, ma tuɣa iṣbeḥ niɣ tuɣa war iḥři.\x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt 1 Kur. 4:5; 2 Kur. 5:10\x* 
